trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 포함 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class is designed to contain a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDisplayModeCollection 클래스의 컬렉션을 포함 하도록 디자인 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control to manage collections of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: 주로 사용 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>의 컬렉션을 관리 하는 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A display mode is a special view of a Web page that appears when it is assigned as the current display mode on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 디스플레이 모드는에 현재 표시 모드도 할당 될 때 표시 되는 웹 페이지의 특수 한 보기 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Display modes are used in the Web Parts control set to create page views in which users can carry out special tasks, such as editing controls, or rearranging the layout of a page.
trans-unit.target: 디스플레이 모드는 사용자가 컨트롤을 편집 하거나 페이지의 레이아웃을 다시 정렬 등의 특수 한 작업을 수행할 수는 페이지 뷰를 설정 하는 웹 파트 컨트롤에 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control defines several display modes, including <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>제어 여러 디스플레이 모드를 포함 하 여 정의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>, 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The collection of display modes is referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 디스플레이 모드의 컬렉션에서 참조 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: On any particular Web page that uses Web Parts controls, only certain display modes are available.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 컨트롤을 사용 하는 특정 웹 페이지에서 특정 디스플레이 모드는 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The default browse mode and the design mode are nearly always available, but the other display modes are available only if their corresponding zone types are present on the page.
trans-unit.target: 디자인 모드 및 기본 찾아보기 모드가 거의 항상 사용할 수 있지만 다른 디스플레이 모드는 해당 영역 형식 페이지에 있는 경우에 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> class overview.
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 참조는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>클래스 개요.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control keeps track of the available display modes on a page with its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>컨트롤이 있는 페이지에 사용 가능한 표시 모드는 추적의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: This property references a WebPartDisplayModeCollection object that contains all the supported display modes.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성에는 모든 지원 되는 디스플레이 모드를 포함 하는 WebPartDisplayModeCollection 개체를 참조 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class does not have an exposed constructor, so you cannot create your own new instance of it.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDisplayModeCollection 클래스에 노출 된 상태로 생성자가 없는 것의 새 인스턴스를 직접 만들 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: If you create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object and want it to be part of the collection of supported display modes in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control, you must inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class, override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> method, call the base method to create the collection, and then add any custom display modes to the collection by using its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정을 만드는 경우 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체 및 지원 되는 디스플레이 모드에서 컬렉션의 일부가 되도록 원하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>컨트롤에서 상속 해야 합니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>클래스, 재정의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A>메서드는 컬렉션을 만드는 기본 메서드를 호출 및 컬렉션에 사용 하 여 모든 사용자 지정 디스플레이 모드를 다음 추가 해당 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class has two public properties.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDisplayModeCollection 클래스에 두 개의 공용 속성이 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> property is a read-only property that indicates whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>속성 컬렉션이 읽기 전용인 지 여부를 나타내는 읽기 전용 속성입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>

trans-unit.source: The overloaded <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A> property provides access to the members of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 오버 로드 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A>속성은 컬렉션의 멤버에 대 한 액세스를 제공 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class also has several methods.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDisplayModeCollection 클래스에는 다음과 같은 몇 가지 메서드가 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> method, already mentioned, enables you to add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects to the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>이미 언급 했 듯이 메서드를 추가할 수 있도록 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체를 컬렉션에.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A> method determines whether a particular display mode exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A>메서드 특정 디스플레이 모드는 컬렉션에 있는지 여부를 확인 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies the collection to an array of objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A>메서드 컬렉션 개체의 배열에 복사 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A> method returns the index of a particular display mode within the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A>메서드는 컬렉션 내에서 특정 디스플레이 모드의 인덱스를 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A> method enables you to insert a display mode object at a particular index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 마지막으로 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A>메서드를 사용 하면 컬렉션의 특정 인덱스에 디스플레이 모드 개체를 삽입할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adds a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 추가 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 개체 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: You can use the Add method to add new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects to an existing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Add 메서드를 사용 하 여 새로 추가 하려면 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체를 기존 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: An example of a scenario in which you would do this is when you create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> class, and you want to add it to the collection of supported display modes on a page.
trans-unit.target: 설정 하려는 시나리오의 예로 사용자 지정을 만들 때 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>클래스 하려면 페이지에서 지원 되는 디스플레이 모드의 컬렉션에 추가 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: To do that, you must inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class and override its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> method, first calling the base method, and then using the Add method to add the custom display mode to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 상속 해야 하는 작업을 수행 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>클래스 다이어그램과 해당 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A>메서드를 먼저 기본 메서드를 호출 하 고 다음 Add 메서드를 사용 하 여 사용자 지정 디스플레이 모드를 컬렉션에 추가 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 컬렉션에 추가 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer value that indicates where the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> was inserted into the collection.
trans-unit.target: 위치를 나타내는 정수 값의 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 컬렉션에 삽입 했습니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 특정 여부를 나타내는 값을 반환 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 개체가 컬렉션에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object and determine whether it is in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Contains 메서드를 사용 하면 특정 확인 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>에 있는지 확인 하 고 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> being checked for its existence in a collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 여부가 확인 되는 컬렉션에 있는지 검색 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether value exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 나타내는 부울 값 여부 value 컬렉션에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 배열에 복사 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array to programmatically manipulate a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: CopyTo 메서드는 프로그래밍 방식으로 집합을 조작 하기 위한 사용자 지정 배열을 만들 때 유용 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: 배열을 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 복사 된 컬렉션을 포함 하는 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: 정수 배열에서 컬렉션의 내용을 배치할 수 있는 시작 지점을 나타내는입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 특정 멤버의 위치를 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects, and you need to know the ordinal position (the index) of one object relative to the others.
trans-unit.target: IndexOf 메서드는 여러 개 있을 경우 유용 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>개체가 서로 기준으로 한 개체의 서 수 위치 (인덱스)를 알고 있어야 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 컬렉션의 멤버입니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 특정 개체의 위치를 나타내는 정수입니다.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object into the collection at the specified index position.
trans-unit.target: 삽입 한 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 개체 컬렉션에서 지정된 된 인덱스 위치에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: If `index` equals the number of items in the collection, then `value` is appended to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 경우 `index` 그런 다음 컬렉션에 있는 항목의 수와 일치 `value` 컬렉션의 끝에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer indicating the ordinal position in the collection at which a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> should be inserted.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 서 수 위치를 나타내는 정수를 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 삽입 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> to insert into the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 를 컬렉션에 삽입 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션이 읽기 전용인 지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The IsReadOnly property value is changed internally by the Web Parts control set as it changes the contents of the collection at different points.
trans-unit.target: IsReadOnly 속성 값이 서로 다른 지점에서 컬렉션의 내용을 변경 될 때 설정 하는 웹 파트 컨트롤에서 내부적으로 변경 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control has added all supported display modes to its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> collection, it internally sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object to read-only to prevent it from being changed.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어 다음은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>컨트롤이 디스플레이 모드를 지원 되는 모든 추가 해당 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A>컬렉션, 내부적으로 설정는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>개체 변경 되지 않도록 방지 하기 위해 읽기 전용입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > There is no mechanism to change this property value from your code, although you can read its value.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 메커니즘은 없습니다 사용자 코드에서이 속성 값을 변경 하려면 해당 값을 읽을 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션이 읽기 전용인 지 여부를 나타내는 부울 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a specific member of the collection according to its index.
trans-unit.target: 해당 항목이 있는 인덱스에 따라 컬렉션의 특정 멤버를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> collection by using an index number that represents its ordinal position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Item 속성을 사용 하면에 액세스 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>내에서 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>컬렉션에서의 서 수 위치를 나타내는 인덱스 번호를 사용 하 여 컬렉션.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the index of a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 멤버의 인덱스를 나타내는 정수입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> 컬렉션에서 지정 된 인덱스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a specific member of the collection according to a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: 고유 식별자에 따라 컬렉션의 특정 멤버를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> collection by using a string identifier for a particular display mode.
trans-unit.target: Item 속성을 사용 하면에 액세스 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>내에서 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>특정 디스플레이 모드에 대 한 문자열 식별자를 사용 하 여 컬렉션.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of a particular display mode in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 특정 디스플레이 모드의 이름을 포함 하는 문자열입니다.

trans-unit.source: The first whose mode name matches the value of the modeName parameter.
trans-unit.target: 첫 번째 모드 이름이 일치의 값은 modeName 매개 변수입니다.
